official documentation available at:
https://www.yoctoproject.org/docs/ → current version
https://www.yoctoproject.org/docs/archived-documents/ → archived versions
Specific for Yocto 2.4.4
https://www.yoctoproject.org/docs/2.4.4/mega-manual/mega-manual.html → everything you need to know about Yocto
https://www.yoctoproject.org/docs/2.4.4/dev-manual/dev-manual.html → focuesed on development
https://www.yoctoproject.org/docs/2.4.4/ref-manual/ref-manual.html → reference: e.g. Yocto standard variables
https://www.yoctoproject.org/docs/2.4.4/sdk-manual/sdk-manual.html → explain differences between SDK and extensible SDK (eSDK)
https://yoctoproject.org/docs/2.4.4/profile-manual/profile-manual.html → system profiling
https://www.yoctoproject.org/docs/2.4.4/kernel-dev/kernel-dev.html → tailored for BSP developers
https://www.yoctoproject.org/docs/2.4.4/bsp-guide/bsp-guide.html → tailored for BSP developers
